ZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #404040; text-decorati=
on: underline;">30% higher rates</a><span> than long-term rentals. Airbnb h=
as even shown a desire to own and manage its own supply with </span><a href=
