ifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #=
404040; text-decoration: underline;">Blackstone&#8217;s Invitation Homes</a=
><span>, on which the private equity firm netted about $7 billion by buying=
