r, Zillbnb would be able to optimize yields based on where each duration pr=
ices in each market.</span></em></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em>Joinin=
g forces with Airbnb might even increase the buyer pool for Zillow&#8217;s =
